metadata.title: Population Dynamics and Stock Assessment of Hatchery-Reared Salmon in Japan
metadata.description: Changes in body size and age composition of adult chum salmon returning to Hokkaido from 1953-present.
metadata.notes:
Purpose: To clarify effects of inter and intra-specific interaction such as carrying capacity and population density and long-term climate change on survival and growth of salmonids in the North Pacific Ocean.
